<lb n="0782a02" ed="B"/>切以繩縣物也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>柺</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0208" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">古買切老人拄杖也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>啐啄</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0218" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">啐即聿切啄竹角切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>圈</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0227" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">丘圓切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>藞苴</form>
<lb n="0782a03" ed="B"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0301" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">藞盧下切莫側下切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>跣</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0310" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">息典切足親地也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>粥薪</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0319" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">粥音育賣也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>罅</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0325" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">呼訝切孔隙也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>茜</form>
<lb n="0782a04" ed="B"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0401" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">倉甸切染絳草名</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><g ref="#CB05218"/></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0409" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">側六切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>砰</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0413" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">披耕切砰磅聲也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><g ref="#CB13283"/></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0421" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">奴<unclear></unclear>切乳也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>臊</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0782a0426" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">蘇高切豕
